data.description: Country Living with the benefits of city access.  Beautiful and energy efficient ranch style home located on 1.848 acres with no HOA fees surrounded by mature oak trees.  A large upstairs room with it's own full bathroom can be used as a rec room or a fifth bedroom.  The backyard is set for entertaining with decking across the entirety of the rear of the house and continuing around the PermaSalt above ground swimming pool.  There is a separate large deck nestled under the canopy of 3 huge live oak trees with refreshing breezes, electricity and low voltage LED lighting to enjoy relaxing evenings.  Only a game fence separates you from a peaceful outcropping of additional live oak trees with the occasional deer, cattle or longhorn resting in their shade on the adjoining property to the rear.    This energy conscious home makes cooling and heating ultra-cost effective with the installation of an enormous solar panel system in 2018, high efficiency HVAC systems in 2019 and solar attic fans in 2021. AVERAGE MONTHLY ELECTRIC BILL WAS $225 (Jul 2022-Jul 2023) for this expansive home.    Other major improvements include a new roof in 2021, a 20x24 workshop with electrical and epoxy floors in 2022, new water heater in 2023, 30 Amp and 50 Amp hookups at the driveway (perfect for charging electric vehicles) and an RV pad with a 50 amp hook up.
